    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely dice the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and chop the <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>green chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 1,
