    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>creamed coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut </strong>and <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>coconut stock </strong>to the pan with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-high and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until the sauce has thickened and the vegetables are tender</p>",
