    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the broccoli is cooking, trim, then chop the <strong>green beans</strong> in half</p><p>Once the <strong>butternut squash </strong>is tender, add the <strong>halved green beans </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to the curry with a splash of <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cook, covered, for a further 6-7 min or until the green beans are tender – this is your <strong>spicy fragrant squash & pistachio curry</strong></p>",
