    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy fragrant squash & pistachio curry </strong>over the <strong>basmati rice </strong>with the <strong>roasted broccoli </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>and <strong>remaining chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into small bowls and turn out</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
